{
  "stem": "1858.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 89.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I remember we were not allowed to wear shoes to school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We had to change in school into a special shoe, because the floors were so gorgeous.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was brand new building, and we were so proud of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And especially the gym room was so different, so new.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were so proud of that school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I adored my teacher, Helen Bergman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I loved school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 9 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was in school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then an announcement came that from that day on, no Jewish child could attend school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a Jewish school, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But nevertheless, schools suddenly were closed to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I cannot begin to describe you what a horrible feeling this is for a child.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First, we thought it was a temporary ordinance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Soon, it will be revoked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, how could you even understand that children would not be allowed-- would be forbidden to attend school?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can we imagine a 9, 10-year-old child stand in front of the house in the morning and observe all my Christian friends who are going to school, carrying books, laughing?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there I stood, helpless, not even understanding why I am not allowed to go to school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was a very painful feeling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But of course, I didn't realize then, in 1939, that for the next six years-- duration of the war-- and two years after, I would never, never be allowed to go to school.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I cannot even describe to you what a horrible feeling this is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I loved school.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still love school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, from the beginning, my mother decided to take a tutor, because we were hoping the schools would open up.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
